# Copy to .env.local and fill in. .env.local is gitignored.
# None of these are required for the initial Vercel deploy — placeholders work,
# the corresponding feature just won't ship until the key is set.

# --- Inner Circle application -------------------------------------------
# /apply is gone — Inner Circle now uses Whop's "Ask questions before
# checkout" feature, which renders the application questions inline in
# the embedded checkout. No env var or server route needed.

# --- Payments + community access ------------------------------------------
# All payments, subscription billing, Discord role assignment, and member
# access flows are handled by Whop's embedded checkout (@whop/checkout/react
# in app/checkout/CheckoutFlow.tsx). Plan IDs are baked into lib/copy.ts.

# --- Founder VSL ---------------------------------------------------------
# Set this to any standard embed URL to drop the founder intro video into
# the VSL section on the home page. When set, the placeholder card is
# replaced with an iframe automatically — no code change needed.
# Examples:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_VSL_URL=https://player.vimeo.com/video/123456789
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_VSL_URL=https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_VSL_URL=https://fast.wistia.com/embed/iframe/abc123def
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VSL_URL=

# --- Error reporting (optional, pick before launch) -----------------------
# SENTRY_DSN=
